<p>Here are my reoccurring/hoping to have reoccurred characters profiles. I’ve been wanting to make them for a while, and I finally got off my ass and did it, aha.</p>
<p>Feel free to use any of them in a tale or SCP! Just let me know in advance, please. :)<br />
